{
	Description = {
		"@eng:Filter mode telling how the sample function will weight the nearby convoluted spectrums\\n - Point : will sample the closest convoluted spectrum. Fastest\\n - Linear : will interpolate between the two nearby convoluted spectrums\\n - Cubic : will smoothly interpolate between the 4 nearby convoluted spectrums. Slowest, best quality, probably totally overkill",
	};
